---
import homeImg from "../../assets/img/abouthome.jpg";
---

<section
  class="px-6 py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"
>
  <!-- Left Image -->
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
    <img
      src={homeImg.src}
      alt="Care and health for everyone"
      class="w-full h-[300px] md:h-[350px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-md"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Right Text -->
  <div
    class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-green-800 text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-wide mb-6"
    >
      Why Families Choose Hospice and Palliative Care of California
    </h2>

    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
      We provide care for individuals at the end of life, offering hospice support shaped around their needs, values, and personal preferences. We take time to understand the person behind the diagnosis by learning their rhythms, their comforts, and the ways they feel most at ease so the care we offer feels personal and supportive. Our clinical team listens closely, collaborates with families and physicians, and shapes care around meaningful details that bring a sense of steadiness and reassurance during a tender time. With 24/7 availability, proactive communication, and a compassionate, delicate approach, we remain at the core of your support system, ensuring your loved one is always cared for.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-800 p-4 mb-6">
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base italic">
        If you choose to get in touch, there is no pressure to begin services. We're here to help you explore your options, understand the hospice process, and offer support at your own pace.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a
      href="#contact"
      class="px-6 py-3 bg-green-800 hover:bg-green-900 text-white font-semibold rounded-3xl transition"
    >
      Request a Free Assessment
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
